# 6. Salesforce Objects Design

## Standard Objects

### Lead

Purpose:
Store prospective customer information.

Key Fields:

| Field Name        | Type     |
| ----------------- | -------- |
| First Name        | Text     |
| Last Name         | Text     |
| Mobile Number     | Phone    |
| Email             | Email    |
| Lead Source       | Picklist |
| Lead Status       | Picklist |
| Preferred Vehicle | Picklist |
| Branch Location   | Picklist |

---

### Account

Purpose:
Store customer account information after lead conversion.

Key Fields:

* Account Name
* Customer Type
* Branch Location

---

### Contact

Purpose:
Store customer contact information.

Key Fields:

* First Name
* Last Name
* Email
* Mobile Number

---

### Opportunity

Purpose:
Track vehicle sales opportunities.

Key Fields:

| Field            | Type     |
| ---------------- | -------- |
| Opportunity Name | Text     |
| Vehicle Model    | Picklist |
| Sales Stage      | Picklist |
| Expected Revenue | Currency |
| Closing Date     | Date     |

---

### Task

Purpose:
Manage follow-up activities.

Key Fields:

* Subject
* Due Date
* Priority
* Status

